{"tid":386914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘋果】我發夢見到三年後摩天輪會變左一棟商廈","createTime":"2017-09-04T09:00:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T00:46:47.000Z","uid":15696,"like":250,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b7abc17e2408d70a07191a4beb2c5b86676fb82","tid":386914,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:00:50.000Z","msg":"蘋果踢爆TECL董事係會德豐大股東女婿：<br />\n<br />\n1. 去年九月，城規會正式通過「中環新海濱第3號用地」的規劃大綱，計劃將約4.76公頃、摩天輪旁邊的3號用地售予私人發展商，與建五個大型商廈。<br />\n<br />\n2. 去年十一月，發展商會德豐的大股東女婿成立公司，今年五月成功招標，成新營運商。<br />\n<br />\n3. 本月，新營運商並暫未公佈會否保留或興建摩天輪(摩天輪僅建議，非必要條件)，政府要求舊營運商拆除摩天輪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下我發夢見到 / 猜測：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 新營運商不打算興建摩天輪，三年來只搞各種短期活動，可能包括AIA嘉年華，用地不時空置。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 三年後政府重新審視，表示結束短約先合乎最大利益，塊地起埋一棟商廈(3號用地相鄰)，由會德豐/其他發展商中標。<br />\n<br />\n3. 現時摩天輪會變左一棟商廈，YEAH！拆唔拆我都贏哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【中環摩天輪】海濱甲級商廈大計上馬 獨家揭新營辦商與九倉吳光正女婿關係<br />\n[url]<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170904/2_545440_0/-%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA-%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E7%94%B2%E7%B4%9A%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%AC-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%AD%E6%96%B0%E7%87%9F%E8%BE%A6%E5%95%86%E8%88%87%E4%B9%9D%E5%80%89%E5%90%B3%E5%85%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%A9%BF%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170904%2F2_545440_0%2F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2591%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25BC%25AA-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2587%259F%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%2580%2589%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A9%25BF%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582&d=2O%2FuI0XC9AMasLbiUOLmrP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=759b8e87\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnextplus%2F%25E6%2599%2582%25E4%25BA%258B%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20170904%2F2_545440_0%2F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2591%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25BC%25AA-%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E6%25BF%25B1%25E7%2594%25B2%25E7%25B4%259A%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%25BB%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%2588%25E4%25B8%258A%25E9%25A6%25AC-%25E7%258D%25A8%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%258F%25AD%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2587%259F%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E5%2595%2586%25E8%2588%2587%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%2580%2589%25E5%2590%25B3%25E5%2585%2589%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A9%25BF%25E9%2597%259C%25E4%25BF%2582&h=87904652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/nextplus/%E6%99%82%E4%BA%8B%E8%A6%81%E8%81%9E/article/20170904/2_545440_0/-%E4%B8%AD%E7%92%B0%E6%91%A9%E5%A4%A9%E8%BC%AA-%E6%B5%B7%E6%BF%B1%E7%94%B2%E7%B4%9A%E5%95%86%E5%BB%88%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%88%E4%B8%8A%E9%A6%AC-%E7%8D%A8%E5%AE%B6%E6%8F%AD%E6%96%B0%E7%87%9F%E8%BE%A6%E5%95%86%E8%88%87%E4%B9%9D%E5%80%89%E5%90%B3%E5%85%89%E6%AD%A3%E5%A5%B3%E5%A9%BF%E9%97%9C%E4%BF%82</a></span>[/url]"},{"pid":"43616ba9a3710f628a350d07de7238c2b5b7a39e","tid":386914,"uid":15696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:02:28.000Z","msg":"冇得鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3fd77b0b9b9107d298a836daf1ff6fbc8c2944","tid":386914,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【圍威喂？起商廈？】《壹週刊》調查獨家發現， 摩天輪新營辦商TECL的董事，竟與發展商會德豐的大股東吳光正之女婿為生意伙伴。事實上，摩天輪的短期租約部分範圍，正正座落於去年獲城規